    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Simply use this to get date before 300 days, replace 300 with your days:</p>\n<pre><code>Date date = new Date(); // Or where ever you get it from\nDate daysAgo = new DateTime(date).minusDays(300).toDate();\n</code></pre>\n<p>Here,</p>\n<p><code>DateTime</code> is <code>org.joda.time.DateTime;</code></p>\n<p><code>Date</code> is <code>java.util.Date</code></p>\n"
  }, {
