    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You may also be able to use the <code>Duration</code> class. E.g.</p>\n<pre><code>Date currentDate = new Date();\nDate oneDayFromCurrentDate = new Date(currentDate.getTime() - Duration.ofDays(1).toMillis());\n</code></pre>\n"
